reviewText: The Concepts are explained at a very very High Level

The course content and instructors were very good.  I had a lot of trouble with getting the exercised working because some capability, e.g. spacy english could not load or for some reason was not detected by the notebook - in local or on WS.  That was the most time consuming part and distracted from the actual work assignment
Basic course and some product use case
It's quite good but the content could be more in-depth as an 'advance' course.
